skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: whiskey tango foxtrot
des: Whiskey Tango Foxtrot is a general purpose voice-only phonetic alphabet translator. With it, you can hear the complete alphabet, you can request the spelling of a word, and you can spell a word in that alphabet to get the word returned. It currently supports the NATO and Western Union phonetic alphabets.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
